    "rationale": "Overall credibility assessment accepted. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 factors meet or exceed required levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted because the COU is explicitly scoped to compression-bending prediction only, model influence is Medium, and the three QoIs all satisfy quantitative acceptance criteria (E/uval < 1.96, percent difference < 10%) across N=11 specimens at two independent laboratories. Project requirements for compression-bending performance are met as documented in the narrative; the FEA modeling framework is deemed sufficiently credible for the stated regulatory decision.",
